quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,69,"Hay so miyamaratiyaya, di niyo zowaa so siran a miziyanta ko Mosa, na piyakakiyas skaniyan o Allah ko pitharo iran: Go miyabaloy sii ko Allah a mmnangan"
  33,70,"Hay so miyamaratiyaya, onoti niyo so Allah, go tharo kano sa katharo a ontol"
  33,71,"Ka tanorn Iyan rkano so manga galbk iyo, go napi Niyan rkano so manga dosa niyo: Na sa taw a onotan iyan so Allah ago so sogo Iyan, na sabnar a miyakadaag sa daag a mala"
  33,72,"Mataan! a Skami na iniayag Ami so sarig ko manga langit go so lopa, go so manga palaw; na da iran pangrawa oba iran oto awidi, go inikalk iran oto: Na inawidan oto o manosiya; - mataan! a skaniyan na aya btad iyan na salimbot, a da a mlng iyan"
  33,73,"Kagiya ziksaan o Allah so manga monapik a manga mama, go so manga monapik a manga babay, go so manga pananakoto a manga mama, go so manga pananakoto a manga babay, go phakatawbatn o Allah so miyamaratiyaya a manga mama, go so miyamaratiyaya a manga babay: Na tatap a so Allah na Manapi, a Makalimoon"